*freeswan-2.04-r1 (01 Jul 2004)

  01 Jul 2004; Jon Hood <squinky86@gentoo.org> freeswan-1.99-r1.ebuild,
  freeswan-2.04-r1.ebuild:
  change virtual/glibc to virtual/libc

  23 Jun 2004; Jay Pfeifer <pfeifer@gentoo.org> freeswan-1.99-r1.ebuild,
  freeswan2.04-r1.ebuild:
  Added x509 updates to fix security issues. Cleaned out older ebuilds.
  Next step is to migrate users off freeswan and on to open/strongswan.

  08 Jun 2004; Michael Sterrett <mr_bones_@gentoo.org> freeswan-1.97.ebuild,
  freeswan-1.98b-r1.ebuild, freeswan-1.98b-r2.ebuild, freeswan-1.98b.ebuild,
  freeswan-2.01.ebuild, freeswan-2.02.ebuild, freeswan-2.03.ebuild:
  clean out older ebuilds

  27 Apr 2004; Aron Griffis <agriffis@gentoo.org> freeswan-1.99.ebuild:
  Add inherit eutils

  20 Feb 2004; Daniel Ahlberg <aliz@gentoo.org> freeswan-1.99.ebuild:
  Patching spi.c, part of #41804.

  06 Feb 2004; Daniel Ahlberg <aliz@gentoo.org>
  files/freeswan-2.02-gentoo.patch, files/freeswan-2.03-gentoo.patch,
  files/freeswan-2.04-gentoo.patch:
  Fix docs dir. Closing #34812.

  03 Jan 2004; Daniel Ahlberg <aliz@gentoo.org> freeswan-2.04.ebuild, freeswan-1.99.ebuild :
  Adding iproute dependency. Closing #35879.

